{"tid":1561613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"從iPhone鬧鐘響起嗰一刻","createTime":"2019-09-11T16:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T07:03:15.000Z","uid":320708,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"536d7041ca6b178bb9c9b38560b58b2f91a584d1","tid":1561613,"uid":320708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"睇iPhone11條宣傳片，真係有些少同感。只不過佢塑造咗一個多姿多彩嘅生活，而我就。。。<br />\n<br />\n每日起身第一件事就係拎起部電話，睇下Facebook有無咩事發生。之後就再始爬TG，爬晒公海，文宣，搜狗等等。以前返工個時都會聽下歌，而家邊搭車邊睇返啲記招，要親耳聽返成個對答內容，怕完全依賴晒新聞會miss咗啲內容。返工無聊開下lihkg，交換下pepe stickers。放工前又爬多次TG睇下邊度有活動。返到屋企就開始研下智慧燈柱呀，黨鐵太子呀同埋新屋嶺疑似身體侵犯呀咁。真係好多嘢要睇，好似返翻去大學做FYP睇papers睇到眼盲。<br />\n<br />\n真心，係攰嘅，但都唔及前線辛苦。唔想無盡嘅譴責令到不公義嘅事沈寂咗。當我以為正苦，狗屋已經誠信破產嘅時候，但不要忘記同温層好厚，仲有好多c9 uncles會覺得班黑衫人係on9嘅係癲嘅要攪亂香港。愈揾得多，揾得清楚啲不公義嘅事實，先可以完全擊破對手。<br />\n<br />\n老土都要講句：<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"f8b550e0256cbeae93a3f3e9c59eeb76fe06d508","tid":1561613,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:05:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6640f5b03a72cafe4f804c09d22bf317e807af85","tid":1561613,"uid":5682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-a